data.description: This well maintained and updated 4 bedroom, 2.5 bathroom Colonial in the desirable Arlington School District is move in ready. Situated on a dead-end road, just minutes to shops and restaurants in the Village of Pleasant Valley. The first floor features an updated eat-in kitchen, half bathroom, laundry room, two massive living rooms and a generously sized dining room. French doors from the kitchen provide access to the enormous stamped concrete patio, in-ground pool area and private fenced-in backyard, perfect for summer barbecues and entertaining. The second set of french doors in the living room provide access to the sunroom complete with floor to ceiling windows and a tile floor, perfect for a greenhouse or lounge area. Going up to the second floor you will find a primary bedroom suite complete with a newly updated full bath and walk in closet. Three additional bedrooms, and a center hall full bath. The two car attached garage and shed in the backyard offer additional storage. This home has too many updates to list, and it will not last. Schedule your showing today!
